Hi,

Forward to 1st, 2nd and 3rd years

Greetings from Planys team!l. Following up on our conversation the other
day, please find the job descriptions for summer internship opportunity at
Planys.

Planys Technologies is an IIT Madras incubated company that provides
immersed structure inspection and survey solutions using indigenously
manufactured remotely operated vehicles. We integrate advanced marine
robotics with the nextgeneration inspection techniques (NDT) to provide a
reliable and safe inspection solution. Website: www.planystech.com.
Currently we provide inspection services at offshore locations (ports,
offshore platform, civil structures etc) and are looking at providing
services for onshore (storage tanks, pipelines) sites and ship hulls. We
have our first vehicle called 'Mike' ready for demonstrations and trials to
end user. Compiled videos of our field trial can be seen on our website &
on our Planys youtube channel
.

Job Description

Role & Responsibilities


    An integral team member in developing a complete software product from
   scratch
    Architecture design and implementation of various modules in the
   software system
    Firmware development for embedded systems in C
    Development of device drivers for hardware systems utilized in ROV
    Computer Network programming and GUI development in Linux environment
    A zeal to learn new technologies, innovate and take responsibilities
   to accomplish initiatives

Requirements:


Recommended Skills:


    Object oriented programming concept
     Intermediate / advanced C, C++ / Python skills
    Advanced concepts in C, C++; IPC, multithreading etc.

Experience: Any practical experience in developing algorithms,
participated in coding competitions.

Stipend: INR 8000 per month.


Location: Chennai



We are looking forward to applications from current 2nd or 3rd year B.Tech
and Dual degree students preferably from Computer Science and
Electrical background. Students from other branches but with prior
experience in the above mentioned domains can apply as well.


Interested students are requested to mail their resume to
careers@planystech.com
<careers@planystech.com with subject as "Application for summer
internship_Software_<Name"


Thank you


 

